<PageLayout
  title="About Litlunches"
  description="What Litlunches is, why it exists"
  schema="AboutPage"
>
    <p>
    Litlunches is a reading guide for language learners who want to read real books,
    not graded readers or simplified texts.
  </p>

  <p>
    The site is built around the idea of comprehensible input: that language is acquired
    through meaningful exposure to messages you can mostly understand, not through
    memorizing rules. Reading fiction is one of the most effective and sustainable
    forms of that exposure.
  </p>
</PageLayout>